  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "BEAUTY SALON DIRECTOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>1. Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Perform eyelash extension and lash lift treatments with high technical standards</li><li>Consult with clients to understand their preferences and recommend suitable designs</li><li>Provide careful, hygienic, and professional services</li><li>Build long-term relationships with clients through high-quality service</li><li>Maintain cleanliness and organization of the treatment area</li></ul><p><strong>2. Professional Background</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum <strong>10 years of experience</strong> as a professional eyelash artist</li><li>Solid experience in classic and volume lash techniques</li><li>Able to work independently and manage treatments without supervision</li><li><strong>Japanese proficiency equivalent to N-1 level</strong>, as many of our clients are Japanese</li><li>Experience working with Japanese customers is highly preferred</li></ul><p><strong>3. Required Qualities</strong></p><ul><li>Detail-oriented and patient, with a strong sense of responsibility</li><li>Calm and professional under pressure</li><li>Passionate about beauty and continuous skill improvement</li><li>Good communication skills and a customer-first mindset</li><li>Respectful, punctual, and reliable</li></ul>",
